keyMappings:
unmapAll

# FIREFOX NATIVE (no dead ends, more responsive)
# ctrl + t | new tab
# ctrl + w | close tab
# ctrl + n | new window
# ctrl + b | bookmarks
# alt + left  | go back
# alt + right | go forward

# VIMIUM
map k scrollUp
map j scrollDown
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map gi focusInput

map f LinkHints.activateMode
map R reload

map w restoreTab
map T duplicateTab
map h previousTab
map l nextTab

map / enterFindMode
map v enterVisualMode
map n performFind
map N performBackwardsFind
map yy copyCurrentUrl

map o Vomnibar.activate
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarks

# map ? showHelp
searchEngines:
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
gm: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s Google maps
